text: In OTH - Level 5 - Sky Garden you can feel the free Nature and good relaxing experience.The Garden is well maintained.You can see the nice views of sun set in the Evening. And also you can see the good views of surrounding Tampines city area. If you want to go leisure walk or need to go to the Exercise I think this place is best for you....🍃🌱🌿🍀☘️🍂🌼🌻🌺🏵️🌸💮🌳🌲🌅👣🏃🧎💚
